-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>请观看下面她在巴黎演唱会中所有现场首演的粉丝镜头。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="泰勒·斯威夫特：Down Bad X Fortnight（The Eras 巡演现场）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/bRrChGbEgsI?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="泰勒·斯威夫特：有史以来最小的人（Eras 巡演现场直播）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/G2VES0GEKgs?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 世界首映：我可以用破碎的心做到这一点 - TTPD The Eras Tour Paris" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/7GC5xllyCYk?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="泰勒·斯威夫特 - loml（Live Eras Tour）9/5/2024" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/BvxWaiUVO7Y?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在演出的其他地方，斯威夫特表演了《残酷的夏天》、《情人》、《无畏》、《爱情故事》、《一切都很好》、《……准备好了吗？》、《羊毛衫》、《风格》等热门歌曲， 《Anti-Hero》和《Karma》还有大量其他深受喜爱的歌曲。</p><h3><strong>这是泰勒·斯威夫特的表演：</strong></h3><p><strong>情人：</strong><br /> <strong>《美国小姐与伤心王子》</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;残酷的夏天&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;男人&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>“你需要冷静下来”</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;情人&#39;</strong></p><p><strong>无畏：</strong><br /> <strong>“无所畏惧”</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;你是属于我